attributes.description:
Created on February 24, 2010 by znzn on Sourcemap.org:

40 linear ft. recycled 6' square extruded aluminum 1/8' thick, 20 linear ft steel plate 1/4' thick and 6' wide, 40 linear feet of recycled aluminum extrusion, 400 sq ft MDF, 400 sq ft white vinyl flooring, 1 laptop, 1 projector, 16sq ft birch plywood 3/4' thick, 2 leather couches with steel frame, 20lbs of non-woven cellulose dyed red and bleached white, 30 sq ft inkjet graphics on PET board
